sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant CDN as Edge CDN
    participant App as App Server
    participant ID as ID Service<br/>(Snowflake)
    participant Cache as KV Cache
    participant DB as Alias Store
    participant ES as Event Stream<br/>(analytics)

    Note over C,ES: Write flow (shorten)
    C->>App: POST /shorten {long_url}
    App->>ID: next_id()
    ID-->>App: snowflake_id
    App->>App: base62(snowflake_id) = alias
    App->>DB: INSERT (alias, long_url)
    DB-->>App: ok
    App->>Cache: SET alias -> long_url (TTL 1h)
    App-->>C: 201 {short_url}

    Note over C,ES: Read flow (redirect)
    C->>CDN: GET /{alias}
    alt CDN cache hit
        CDN-->>C: 301 Location: long_url
    else CDN miss
        CDN->>App: forward
        App->>Cache: GET alias
        alt cache hit
            Cache-->>App: long_url
        else cache miss
            App->>DB: SELECT long_url WHERE alias
            DB-->>App: long_url
            App->>Cache: backfill
        end
        App-)ES: click event (fire-and-forget)
        App-->>CDN: 301 + Cache-Control
        CDN-->>C: 301 Location: long_url
    end
